=======================================
H_ThinFilmInterference - PUBLIC RELEASE
=======================================
By Ryan Hussain
ryan@splicer.tv

Thin Film Interference utility shader for Mantra and Arnold renderers, based on the following papers by Andrew Glassner.

Glassner, A., "Soap bubbles. 1," Computer Graphics and Applications, IEEE , vol.20, no.5, pp.76,84, Sep/Oct 2000
URL: http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/stamp/stamp.jsp?tp=&arnumber=865884&isnumber=18744

Glassner, A., "Soap bubbles. 2 [Computer graphics]," Computer Graphics and Applications, IEEE , vol.20, no.6, pp.99,109, Nov/Dec 2000
URL: http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/stamp/stamp.jsp?tp=&arnumber=888023&isnumber=19197


Notes:
    This public release is for non-commercial demonstration and demo purposes and does not include the full shading model implementation of the privately maintained H_ThinFilmInterference models.


Contributers:
